Horn Pipe Layback Recycler Rig

Description for Part Number 6110

Scroll Thru Images to See a Function Video!

A laidback, or layback style rig, for a laidback dab session! A nice, pivoted mouthpiece headed in the right direction makes this pipe comfortable to use. This horn-shaped recycler rig keeps the terps bouncing off of the very ample bubble stack that will occur above the inline slit percolator, cooling and preserving the flavors. Recyclers are great for maximizing the terp profile of your oil. There are three color accented glass grip bubbles on the starboard side for convenience, and the 14mm female pipe joint is ultra-rugged. Recyclers provide really smooth dabs and help to keep coughing to a minimum, while also providing some visual fun, watching the recycled water "drain" back into the base.
